      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Asking 'Is there...?'"
        },
        "text": "To ask if something exists or is available, you can use 'فيه...؟' (fee...?). This is very common.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "فيه صيدلية قريبة من هنا؟",
            "english": "Is there a pharmacy near here?",
            "transliteration": "Fee saydaliya qareeba min hena?"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "فيه تاكسي؟",
            "english": "Is there a taxi?",
            "transliteration": "Fee taksi?"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Asking 'How can I go to...?'"
        },
        "text": "For specific directions to a place, use 'إزاي أروح لـ...؟' (ezayy arooḥ li...?). 'إزاي' means 'how', 'أروح' means 'I go', and 'لـ' is 'to'.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "إزاي أروح للمستشفى؟",
            "english": "How can I go to the hospital?",
            "transliteration": "Ezayy arooḥ lel-mostashfa?"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "إزاي أروح للسوبر ماركت؟",
            "english": "How can I go to the supermarket?",
            "transliteration": "Ezayy arooḥ les-supermarket?"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Asking for Help: 'Can you help me?'"
        },
        "text": "If you are lost or need assistance, you can politely ask 'ممكن تساعدني؟' (momken tesa'edni?) for a male, or 'ممكن تساعديني؟' (momken tesa'edeeni?) for a female. 'ممكن' means 'possible' or 'can I/you'.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "لو سمحت، ممكن تساعدني؟",
            "english": "Excuse me (if you please), can you help me? (asking a male)",
            "transliteration": "Law samaḥt, momken tesa'edni?"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "ممكن تساعديني ألاقي البنك؟",
            "english": "Can you help me find the bank? (asking a female)",
            "transliteration": "Momken tesa'edeeni ala'i el-bank?"
          }
        ]
      }
